cover the truth about their relationship, and come up with a plan to switch places in an effort to reunite their mother and father.","genre_ids":[35,10751,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":9.3244,"vote_count":4449,"poster_path":"/dNqgjqxHIdfsQRQL5XTujNfX9pj.jpg","release_date":"1998-07-28","vote_average":7.217,"backdrop_path":"/y3zUOMWRoI2vC4ck2GBJyFWhzyA.jpg","original_title":"The Parent Trap","original_language":"en"},{"id":1397832,"adult":false,"title":"A Widow's Game","video":false,"overview":"When a man is found dead, the investigation shatters his widow's perfect facade and exposes a hidden double life in this thriller based on real events.","genre_ids":[53,9648],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.0483,"vote_count":257,"poster_path":"/yZOdrJDl2GwREoigC0y40kMosxj.jpg","release_date":"2025-05-30","vote_average":6.245,"backdrop_path":"/pOR4Aye28KLZ5Jogu8zc3yiqBpT.jpg","original_title":"La viuda negra","original_language":"es"},{"id":666277,"adult":false,"title":"Past Lives","video":false,"overview":"After decades apart, childhood friends Nora and Hae Sung are reunited in New York for one fateful weekend as they confront notions of destiny, love, and the choices that make a life.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":7.4476,"vote_count":2203,"poster_path":"/k3waqVXSnvCZWfJYNtdamTgTtTA.jpg","release_date":"2023-06-02","vote_average":7.718,"backdrop_path":"/7HR38hMBl23lf38MAN63y4pKsHz.jpg","original_title":"Past Lives","original_language":"en"},{"id":872585,"adult":false,"title":"Oppenheimer","video":false,"overview":"The story of J. Robert Oppenheimer's role in the development of the atomic bomb during World War II.","genre_ids":[18,36],"media_type":"movie","popularity":22.2091,"vote_count":11373,"poster_path":"/8Gxv8gSFCU0XGDykEGv7zR1n2ua.jpg","release_date":"2023-07-19","vote_average":8.035,"backdrop_path":"/ycnO0cjsAROSGJKuMODgRtWsHQw.jpg","original_title":"Oppenheimer","original_language":"en"},{"id":792307,"adult":false,"title":"Poo